flowchart TD
    tool[工具调用请求]

    tool --> check1{在白名单中?}
    check1 -->|是| allow_fast[直接放行\nisAutoModeAllowlistedTool = true]
    check1 -->|否| check2{toAutoClassifierInput\n返回空字符串?}
    check2 -->|是| allow_skip[跳过安全检查\n写入 transcript 时忽略]
    check2 -->|否| classify[构建 transcript\n调用 AI 分类器]
    classify --> result["ClassifierResult\n{shouldBlock, confidence, reason}"]
    result -->|shouldBlock=false| allow_final[放行]
    result -->|shouldBlock=true| deny[拒绝或询问用户]
